285
00:19:18,989 --> 00:19:21,290
Lihat aku baik-baik.

286
00:19:22,019 --> 00:19:23,759
Kamu akan tahu.

287
00:19:23,759 --> 00:19:26,090
Lihat aku sekarang.

288
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:28,659
Kamu mengenaliku, bukan?

289
00:19:28,659 --> 00:19:29,729
Kamu siapa?

290
00:19:38,939 --> 00:19:40,439
Anda tersesat lagi?

291
00:19:40,439 --> 00:19:42,239
Tidak.

292
00:19:42,239 --> 00:19:44,280
