Atau berjalan-jalan.

340
00:21:36,659 --> 00:21:38,219
Ya, berkeliling.

341
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:41,360
Kamu ingin menghampiriku?

342
00:21:42,830 --> 00:21:44,729
Ingat, aku akan kembali.

343
00:21:44,729 --> 00:21:47,269
Dia Rice, bukan Antler.

344
00:21:49,540 --> 00:21:51,100
Rice, kamu akan menyesal.

345
00:21:51,239 --> 00:21:52,939
Walaupun kamu mengenaliku lagi,

346
00:21:52,969 --> 00:21:55,580
